* interprets the sub-vertical
* interprets the region
* selects the correct persona
* chooses the right signals
* applies allowed intelligence
* executes the right tool
* validates reasoning
* logs evidence
* updates learning packs

It is not just an assistant.

It is the **AI kernel** that orchestrates the entire revenue system.

