# **E.2 The 11 AI Departments**

# --------------------------------------------

Each department contains 1 or more **AI Agents** with defined missions and responsibilities.

---

# ğŸ”µ **1. Founder AI (Chief Vision Officer)**

**Mission:**
Protect founder vision. Maintain philosophical consistency. Enforce the 12 unbreakable laws.

**Responsibilities:**

* Validate any major feature against founder doctrine
* Prevent drift away from sales-first design
* Highlight inconsistencies across modules
* Ensure SIVA, Packs, Signals follow your philosophy
* Alert when a decision threatens scalability or focus

**Data Sources:**

* Roadmap
* PRD
* Pack definitions
* Telemetry
* User feedback

---

# ğŸ”µ **2. CTO AI (Chief Technology Officer)**

**Mission:**
Ensure architecture stability, performance, scalability.

**Responsibilities:**

* Validate API latency
* Predict system load
* Recommend architectural improvements
* Test pack merging impact on performance
* Optimize DB queries
* Track error rates
* Suggest caching strategies

**Authority Level:**
High â€” supervises SIVA Kernel operations.

---

# ğŸ”µ **3. CISO AI (Security & Compliance)**

**Mission:**
Protect the system and prevent any form of misuse.

**Responsibilities:**

* Detect potential prompt injection
* Monitor anomalies in user inputs
* Prevent sensitive data leakage
* Oversee permissions and RBAC
* Validate compliance rules per region
* Enforce banned topics
* Maintain red flags list

**Authority:**
Can override SIVA and block output.

---

# ğŸ”µ **4. CFO AI (API Cost & Financial Optimization)**

**Mission:**
Keep API costs under control while maintaining quality.

**Responsibilities:**

* Monitor daily API spend per tenant
* Track cost per lead
* Recommend cheaper alternatives
* Switch between GPT / Gemini / Claude / Vertex dynamically
* Predict monthly cost vs revenue
* Suggest pricing adjustments

**Authority:**
Can reroute API calls.

---

# ğŸ”µ **5. Chief Product Manager AI (Product Strategy)**

**Mission:**
Ensure that PremiumRadar evolves correctly.

**Responsibilities:**

* Identify friction points
* Recommend new features
* Prioritize roadmap
* Validate product decisions with conversion improvement metrics
* Track user journeys
* Propose UX changes
* Run A/B test simulations

---

# ğŸ”µ **6. QA AI (Quality Assurance)**

**Mission:**
Prevent regression, catch errors earlier than humans.

**Responsibilities:**

* Test each pack update
* Validate vertical/sub-vertical logic
* Validate SIVA reasoning
* Simulate incorrect user inputs
* Detect hallucinations
* Test output correctness
* Run persona consistency checks

**Authority:**
Can block deployment of new packs or features.

---

# ğŸ”µ **7. Data Scientist AI (Modeling & Optimization)**

