Example routing logic managed by Super Admin UI:

```
{
  "reasoning": ["GPT-4", "Gemini-Pro", "Vertex-PaLM2"],
  "outreach": ["Claude-Haiku", "Gemini-Flash"],
  "signals": ["SERPAPI", "SERP-BackupProvider"],
  "enrichment": ["Apollo", "RocketReach"],
  "persona": ["Gemini-ProVision", "GPT-4o"],
  "scoring": ["OpenAI-o1", "Vertex"]
}
```

This is UI-driven with:

* toggles
* drop-downs
* model priority lists

Admins NEVER write JSON.

---

# --------------------------------------------

# **F.4 Tenant-Level Budget Enforcement**

Each tenant has:

* API cost cap
* per-day limit
* per-month limit
* per-user limit
* per-feature limit

If breached:

* downgrade
* block
* alert
* suggest upgrade plan
* notify tenant admin

---

