| Plan       | Max Enrichments | Max Discoveries | LLM Budget | Priority |
| ---------- | --------------- | --------------- | ---------- | -------- |
| Individual | 200/month       | 100/month       | Low        | Low      |
| Pro        | 1,000/month     | 500/month       | Medium     | Medium   |
| Enterprise | 100,000/month   | 50,000/month    | High       | High     |

This is automatic and enforced by the API OS.

