# **H.3 Tenant Profile Structure (Internal Schema)**

Every tenant has a structured definition:

```
{
  "tenantId": "ENBD_001",
  "type": "enterprise",
  "region": "UAE",
  "verticalsEnabled": ["Banking", "Corporate Banking", "Mortgage"],
  "subVerticalOverrides": {
      "Employee Banking": { ... },
      "Corporate Banking": { ... }
  },
  "persona": {
      "tone": "formal-banking",
      "style": "professional-advisory",
      "brandRules": []
  },
  "compliance": {
      "forbiddenPhrases": [...],
      "restrictedTopics": [...],
      "customBoundaries": [...]
  },
  "apiBudget": {
      "monthlyLimit": 2000,
      "perUserLimit": 100,
      "alertsEnabled": true
  },
  "campaigns": [...],
  "users": [...],
  "contextOverrides": {...}
}
```

Admins NEVER see JSON â€” UI only.

