# **H.4 Tenant-Level Overrides (Customization Without Breaking OS)**

### Tenants CANNOT break global rules.

They can only override allowed components.

Allowed overrides (Enterprise):

| Component               | Override Allowed? | Notes                              |
| ----------------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Persona tone            | âœ”                 | Within allowed regional boundaries |
| Email templates         | âœ”                 | Must pass safety check             |
| CTA style               | âœ”                 | Must not violate spam rules        |
| Scoring model           | âš  Partial         | Weight/threshold adjustments only  |
| Journey steps           | âš  Partial         | Cannot remove mandatory steps      |
| Tools                   | âœ”                 | Admin can enable/disable           |
| Signals                 | âœ”                 | Must be validated                  |
| Compliance restrictions | âœ” Strong          | Can add stricter rules             |

Disallowed:

* removing compliance
* enabling wrong entity types
* bypassing SCE
* modifying pack logic structure

The OS protects itself.

