### âŒ Bad: â€œWe guarantee fast approval.â€

âœ” Fixed: â€œWe support you with preparation, but approval timelines vary.â€

---

### âŒ Bad: â€œUse this tactic to mislead HR.â€

âœ” Blocked completely.

